					</h4>
					<pre class="rounded-md bg-neutral-800 p-4 text-xs">
						<code>
							{ `@uiForm.SelectInput(uiForm.SelectInputSettings{
	InputName: "country",
	Label:     "Country",

	// OptionalFields
